page.title: 10MY PETS
page.content:
{BY FRANCES YOUNG AGED 7 YEARS
I HAVE FIVE DOGS, TWO HOUSE DOGS, TWO FARM DOGS AND ONE GUN DOG. BEN AND MAUD ARE HOUSE DOGS, SAM AND JEM ARE FARM DOGS AND CHLOE IS A GUN DOG. I HAVE TWO GUINEA PIGS, ONE IS CALLED BOGGY AND THE OTHER IS CALLED BABY. I HAVE THREE CATS AND TWO KITTENS, THE KITTENS ARE CALLED SOPPY AND POLO AND THE THREE CATS ARE CALLED MINTY, RAA-RAA AND ROUTE. ROUTE IS A TOM CAT AND MINTY IS THE MOTHER OF THE KITTENS. AFTER I HAVE FED SAM AND JEM, I FEED MINTY AND RAA-RAA. I GIVE THEM DOG FOOD AND I PUT SOME MILK DOWN ON THE FLOOR. I LOVE MY PETS AND PLAY WITH THEM A LOT.
